        <text>
            <body>
                
                                        <p>Ego <persName key="d1e13219" xml:id="d1e136600">Petrus, Dei gratia <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284001" xml:id="d1e136602">sancti Benigni
                                Divionensis</orgName> abbas et domini <persName key="himanis_324599" xml:id="d1e136605">Manasse episcopi <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#317574" xml:id="d1e136607">Lingonensis</placeName>
                            </persName> vicarius</persName>, notifico pre<lb n="2" break="no"/>sentibus et futuris quod duo fratres de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324466" xml:id="d1e136613">Lania</placeName>, <persName key="d1e13225" xml:id="d1e136616">Matheus</persName> videlicet et <persName key="d1e13231" xml:id="d1e136619">Arnulfus</persName>, invadiaverunt
                        fratribus de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e136623">Fonteneto</orgName>
                        <lb n="3"/> partem suam pasturarum de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324466" xml:id="d1e136627">Lania</placeName> pro .XX. libris, tali conditione
                        quod nisi de propriis denariis eam redimere non poterunt <lb n="4"/> nec ab
                        altero redimi facient. Cum vero eam redemerint alteri vendere vel invadiare
                        eandem non poterunt, nisi prius <lb n="5"/> eosdem fratres inde
                        submonuerint. Quod si idem fratres tantum inde eis dare noluerint quantum ab
                        altero eis oblatum fuerit, <lb n="6"/> exinde cuicumque placuerit eis
                        vendere aut invadiare licebit. Quamdiu autem jamdicti fratres eandem
                        pasturam <lb n="7"/> habuerint, ipsi videlicet <persName key="d1e13237" xml:id="d1e136639">Matheus</persName> et <persName key="d1e13243" xml:id="d1e136642">Arnulfus</persName> eis adversus omnes homines si
                        necesse fuerit guarentiam portabunt <lb n="8"/> nec aliorum animalia nisi
                        sua aut hominum suorum propria pascere ibi permittent, sed ad usus animalium
                            <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e136647">Fonteneti</orgName>
                        fideliter <lb n="9"/> eam defendent. Et sciendum quod postquam eadem
                        guageria redempta fuerit, animalia fratrum quadraginta diebus <lb n="10"/>
                        post redemptionem in eadem pastura libere et quiete sine ulla calumpnia
                        pasturabunt. Hec autem omnia <lb n="11"/> isdem <persName key="d1e13250" xml:id="d1e136657">Matheus</persName> super sancta juravit se per omnia
                        fideliter custodire. Hujus rei testes sunt <persName key="d1e13256" xml:id="d1e136660">Walterius de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324468" xml:id="d1e136662">Ar<lb n="12" break="no"/>genteolo</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13262" xml:id="d1e136667">Robertus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324352" xml:id="d1e136669">Riceio</placeName>
                        </persName> et <persName key="d1e13268" xml:id="d1e136672">Thomas</persName>
                        frater ejus, <persName key="d1e13274" xml:id="d1e136676">Silvester
                            prepositus <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#101449" xml:id="d1e136678">Tornodori</placeName>
                        </persName>, et <persName key="d1e13280" xml:id="d1e136681">Adam</persName>
                        nepos ejus. <lb n="13"/> Hoc totum laudavit <persName key="d1e13287" xml:id="d1e136686">Lora</persName> uxor ejusdem <persName key="d1e13293" xml:id="d1e136689">Mathei</persName>. Unde testes sunt <persName key="d1e13299" xml:id="d1e136692">Rocelinus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324466" xml:id="d1e136694">Lania</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13305" xml:id="d1e136698">Thomas <lb n="14"/>
                            de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324352" xml:id="d1e136702">Riceio</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13311" xml:id="d1e136705">Hugo</persName>
                        filius <persName key="d1e13317" xml:id="d1e136708">Pagani de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324466" xml:id="d1e136710">Lania</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13324" xml:id="d1e136713">Clarus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324466" xml:id="d1e136715">Lania</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13330" xml:id="d1e136718">Hugo
                                <foreign>Billart</foreign>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e13336" xml:id="d1e136723">Raimbaudus de <lb n="15"/>
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324944" xml:id="d1e136726">Marcennaco</placeName>
                        </persName>. Actum anno incarnationis Domini millesimo centesimo
                        nonagesimo.</p>
                
